sentences: Zomby is a British electronic musician who began releasing music in 2007.
Zomby's first major release was the Zomby EP in 2008 on the Hyperdub label.
In 2009, he released a subsequent collection of tracks, One Foot Ahead of the Other.
In 2011, Zomby signed to 4AD Records, on which he released Dedication, also in 2011.
In 2013, Zomby released a double album, entitled With Love.
On 9 October 2015, Zomby released 'Let's Jam 1 & 2' on XL Recordings.
Zomby's fourth album, Ultra, was released on the Hyperdub label in September 2016.
In early 2012, UK producer Reark posted a loop to SoundCloud entitled "Natalia's Song" he claimed to have written in 2007 and that Zomby had plagiarised.
